uk.ac.aber.group14.model

Class PointOfInterest

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.aber.group14.model.PointOfInterest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPointOfInterest

    public class PointOfInterest
extends java.lang.Object
implements IPointOfInterest
    This class is an implementation if IPointOfInterest. It stores a String name, String description, Location object, and a String for the URI of the picture on the filesystem
